config BR2_PACKAGE_QRTR_EXT
	bool "qrtr"
	help
	  Qualcomm IPC Router (QRTR) userspace: libqrtr and the
	  qrtr-ns name service daemon (plus qrtr-cfg, qrtr-lookup).

	  qrtr-ns provides QMI service discovery, required for the DSP
	  subsystems to register their protection-domain "servreg"
	  service. Without it the DSP rootPD never finishes coming up
	  and FastRPC stalls with a GLINK intent timeout.

	  https://github.com/linux-msm/qrtr
